# Canonical host: apex (aisectools.dev)
# www.aisectools.dev → aisectools.dev
# Note: fires only if www is also configured as a custom domain on the Pages project.
# The *.pages.dev preview domain is handled by an account-level Bulk Redirect
# (Cloudflare Dashboard → Bulk Redirects), since _redirects does not apply to
# the Pages-managed pages.dev hostname.
https://www.aisectools.dev/* https://aisectools.dev/:splat 301
http://www.aisectools.dev/* https://aisectools.dev/:splat 301
